- Outcome / user value: Product and engineering can sequence a coherent fix for board switching and numeric selector behavior without bundling unrelated UI risks into one oversized story.
- Scope notes: In scope, splitting the intake into child stories for active-work switch protection, numeric naming enforcement, numeric ordering, and invalid current-sprint recovery after board changes. Out of scope, carrying this work as one implementation ticket or redesigning unrelated board navigation behavior.
- Acceptance criteria:
